"{\"uid\": \"si.com-golf-mens-womens-olympic-golf-gear-paris-2024\", \"text\": \"This post contains affiliate links, where we may receive a percentage of any sale made from the links on this page. Prices and availability are accurate as of the time of publication.  The U.S. Olympic golf teams are set and ready for the 2024 Summer Olympic Games. Here at home all eyes will be watching Collin Morikawa, Scottie Scheffler, Wyndham Clark, Rose Zhang and Lilia Vu among others, as they compete on the world stage. Along with teammates Nelly Korda and Xander Schauffele who will look to repeat winning gold medals from the last games, the competition will no doubt create memory-making moments.\\u00c2  We will also be checking out what the Team USA participants are wearing at the host venue, Le Golf National in France, which was also the site of the 2018 Ryder Cup. Sports fashion apparel brand, J. Lindeberg got the nod to be USA golf\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s official outfitter this week and the 2028 Olympics in Los Angeles.  With the opening ceremonies rapidly approaching, we take a closer look at a few key fashion favorites in the J. Lindeberg Olympic Collection which is not only for the teams, but available to all of us armchair athletes as well.\\u00c2  Get the best prices on J. Lindeberg's Olympic Collection through our partner's at PGA TOUR Superstore  Get the best price on the Emeric polo through our partners at PGA TOUR Superstore  Get the Lamia sweatshirt here through our partners at PGA TOUR Superstore  These items plus belts, sun sleeves,golf bags, bucket hat, socks, towel, backpack, phone case, shoe bag and more, are all part of the J. Lindeberg USA Golf Collection, available at\\u00c2jlindebergusa.com\\u00c2\\u00a0and select pieces at\\u00c2pgatoursuperstore.com.\\u00c2    Loading recommendations... Please wait while we load personalized content recommendations  Janice Ferguson helped start/write the Apparel Wire for Golf Press Association\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0094the first 